{"tid":1434117,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果想再搞一次和理非大遊行, 建議可以揀香港重光紀念日","createTime":"2019-08-08T16:23:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T16:51:42.000Z","uid":277621,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cea4f6465fed896a7e2ecfbebdd537caacd2a383","tid":1434117,"uid":277621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:23:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%87%8D%E5%85%89%E7%B4%80%E5%BF%B5%E6%97%A5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2587%258D%25E5%2585%2589%25E7%25B4%2580%25E5%25BF%25B5%25E6%2597%25A5&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCEtjIx4W8g%2FGk507jgkcous%3D&h=735bf8c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%87%8D%E5%85%89%E7%B4%80%E5%BF%B5%E6%97%A5</a><br />\n1946年，港英政府將8月30日定為「重光紀念日」（曾譯作光復紀念日），並列入香港公眾假期，以紀念英國於1945年8月30日正式重新管治香港，並悼念在香港保衞戰為香港捐軀的將士。1968年，紀念日改定於8月第一個星期一及8月最後的星期一。1983年，紀念日改定於8月最後的星期一之前一個星期六、及8月最後的星期一。<br />\n<br />\n香港重光紀念日, 97後被取消的假期, 但今時今日, 呢日變得非常有意義, 眼下香港在暴政下, 極需要重光, 光復香港, 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n8月30日係星期五, 可以定8月31星期六遊行, 仲可以去遮打道和平紀念碑做d 儀式, 紀念抗爭以嚟犠牲左的義士, 同為抗爭再誓師, 發表宣言<br />\n<br />\n小小愚見, 拋磚引玉"},{"pid":"39b821b414def606f49c62650a5e6f191aaf6198","tid":1434117,"uid":277621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:24:30.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"5209f7b519651b3797cdee0d5250107c3bff710b","tid":1434117,"uid":155462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:24:51.000Z","msg":"可以"},{"pid":"caba205a59d7325f4d64d9aba8e9cc6acf6e1fc3","tid":1434117,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:25:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3daadfd4ebd17b21d530388a99575a20660a1cc6","tid":1434117,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T16:26:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b7f0e895108ba12a3a15566c6faf1e7b56c2a89d","tid":1434117,"uid":277621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"